Notes:
  - negative_pct: % of mutations with fitness < 0 (deleterious)
  - positive_pct: % of mutations with fitness > 0 (beneficial)
  - neutral_pct: % of mutations with |fitness| < 0.1 (near-neutral)
  - strong_negative_pct: % with fitness < -1 (>50% reduction)
  - strong_positive_pct: % with fitness > 1 (>2× improvement)
